The Source Code contains 3 main parts:

- Main Process: main.cpp, main.h, extCommon.h, extOpencvHeader.h
  + extCommon.h contains predefined constants to configure the whole system
  + extOpencvHeader.h contains included opencv headers

- Image Processing: ImgProcessing.cpp, ImageProcessing.h, cameraFrameWork.cpp, cameraFrameWork.h
  + ImageProcessing.h all the defined image processing functions
  + cameraFrameWork.h read the input sequence with various types of input: folder of images, video or static image

- Supporting Function: Line.h, my_tools.cpp, my_tools.h
  + the math functions that are used to support image processing function.

